Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although smaller, my mind\Nremains that of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case is about John the dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a shepherd dog known\Nthroughout the neighborhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogs may not speak, but\Nthere's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John the Dog's Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how old he is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was still just a\Npuppy when I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd say around 8 or so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John. I'm not high school\Nstudent Kudo Shinichi anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grade school student\NConan Edogawa now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Several days later
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since we ate out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That restaurant was pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is the place!\NThe house where John the dog lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were in grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi used to stop by here\Non his way home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would save some bread from\Nlunch and then give it to the dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaguchi Masayoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that name somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a famous lawyer who\Nspecializes in cases involving minors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this the house where that\Nmiddle school student killed himself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was in third grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped at Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? What's going on,\NTakeshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in Izu on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard Takeshi-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}scream-- what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come home right away!\NJohn's done something terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was Maehara\NTakeshi, twenty-two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a college student who lives\Nin the apartment complex next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Sakaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}asked him to\Nwatch the place while he was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Takeshi-{\i1}san {\i0}invited you,\NSugita Sanae-{\i1}san{\i0}, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, could you give us the\Ndetails about what exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was around 8:00 when I came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been in\Nsuch a huge living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just getting fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaguchi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? John?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's at the top of the stairs,\Nbehaving himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You want to talk to John?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John! Hey, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your master\Nwants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would\Nthe dog suddenly attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only think that he attacked\NTakeshi for no reason at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! John would never\Nattack anyone for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Takeshi didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen\Nto the dog, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say anything for sure yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if he really attacked\Nfor no reason as she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then he'll probably\Nhave to be put to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put to sleep?\NYou're going to kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we first need\Nto talk to Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"First year middle school\Nstudent kills himself."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Was bullying the cause?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...a classmate that\Nbullied Masato-{\i1}kun{\i0}--"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't give the bully's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John's been well trained,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he'd never attack\Nanyone for no reason at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John attacked the victim immediately\Nafter the phone was put to his ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Sakaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}ordered\NJohn to attack over the phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sakaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}always seems\Nso nice; he'd never do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's John, Inspector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't put him\Nto sleep already, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been taken to\Nthe police station for now;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it hasn't been decided that\Nhe's to be put to sleep yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Inspector.\NWhat did Sakaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he can't believe\Nthat John would attack anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither can I!\NThere must be a reason why--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Mr. Sakaguchi\Nabout his phone conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start off, what exactly did\Nyou say to the victim over the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him if everything\Nwas alright, how John was doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I asked him\Nto put John on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always say good night to him,\Nso I thought I'd say it tonight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you told John good night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, I think I asked,\N"How are you doing, John?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then suddenly I heard\NJohn bark and Takeshi-{\i1}kun {\i0}scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaguchi-{\i1}san\N{\i0}didn't say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who was\Nthere confirmed his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned it last night,\Ndidn't you, Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:09:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s son\Ncommitted suicide a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him about\Nthat at the station too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said a bully drove him to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe his son's bully\Nwas Maehara Takeshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still just a "maybe."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this directly\Nfrom Sakaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His son Masato-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}and Maehara Takeshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were classmates in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato-{\i1}kun {\i0}apparently wrote\Nabout Takeshi-{\i1}kun {\i0}in his diary
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shortly before\Nhanging himself in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that Mr. Sakaguchi loathed\NTakeshi-{\i1}kun {\i0}after reading the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since his wife had died early on,\NMasato-{\i1}kun {\i0}was all he had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he saw Takeshi-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}crying and apologizing at the funeral,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he decided to forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi-{\i1}kun {\i0}was the only\None who bullied Masato-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly after, Takeshi-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}moved to western Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of his father's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, two years ago, he moved\Nback to attend a university in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was this spring that he\Nmoved into an apartment complex
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right next to the Sakaguchi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly was an act of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Mr. Sakaguchi was\Nsurprised by the unexpected reunion, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he no longer bore any\Nill feelings toward Takeshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even told that he sometimes\Ninvited him over for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he really does still\Nhave a grudge against Takeshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sakaguchi secretly\Ntrained John to attack people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when a specific phrase is said to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then last night, he said\Nthat phrase to John over the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this way, Mr. Sakaguchi\Naccomplished his revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I questioned him last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he repeated what he said on\Nthe phone, right in front of John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John didn't react one\Nbit when he heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! I thought\NI sounded so authoritative too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel so down\Nin the dumps, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be lonely\Nwithout John to keep you company!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, does John always\Nsleep at the top of the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't he sleep downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that door there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my son's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He absolutely loved John.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his late mother said he\Ncouldn't let the dog in his room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so John always\Nslept in front of his door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John's still waiting for him to open\Nthe door and say good morning to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's been\Neight years since my son died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big phone over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The receiver's\Nconnected to it by a cord...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, wasn't there a\Ncordless phone there last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I sometimes switch\Nit with the phone in my study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy really did--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock must've struck\N9:00 just before it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see how Sakaguchi-{\i1}san\N{\i0}ordered John to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone was different?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The receiver on the big\Nphone is connected by a cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But last night he had a\Ncordless phone there, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? There's\Nprobably no real reason--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}absolutely\Nneeded it to be a cordless phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. It would be impossible to\Ncarry a regular phone up a staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sakaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}purposely\Nplaced a portable cordless phone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you still think that Sakaguchi-{\i1}san\N{\i0}used John to commit a murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely certain of it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know the most important thing--\Nhow he ordered the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, our clock doesn't chime, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock in Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Nliving room chimes real loud every hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His clock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was precisely 9:00 when\NJohn attacked Takeshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great detective, Mori Kogoro,\Nhas just solved the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little test.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I give the word,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,repeat what you said to\NJohn last night on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were my deductions all wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so certain of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You overanalyzed things, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would never use the dog\Nthat his son loved to get revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say anything for certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what we found out\Nfrom our investigation afterward
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was that Sakaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}supposedly\Ntook John somewhere in his car
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every Sunday for the last three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to him, he took\NJohn to the outskirts of town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let him get a lot of\Nexercise in the empty fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! He obviously\Ntrained John during those times!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sorry to have to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's been decided that John\Nis to be put to sleep tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sakaguchi understands as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John, the dog you liked so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is going to be killed\Nif we don't do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can save John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're going\Nto kill John this evening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was up all night\Nthinking about it too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think he figured out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to have another test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now say the words, if you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you admit you trained\NJohn to attack Maehara Takeshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't remember anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't remember me, or Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had completely forgotten about\Nthe very person he drove to suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he unwittingly moved\Ninto the apartment complex next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lawyer who specializes\Nin crimes committed by minors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took this job so that I could\Nhelp young people who lost their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when I saw him crying and\Napologizing at the funeral eight years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was still just a\N1st-year middle school student,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I felt that Masato's\Ndeath wouldn't be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if he truly regretted it\Nwith all his heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I met him\Nagain eight years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he didn't remember a\Nsingle thing about the incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, he was no\Ndifferent than he was eight years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my wallet back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just borrowing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying! I'll pay you back\None of these days, when I feel like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows when that'll be, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw that,\NI could feel my blood boil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was Masato's death for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I ever forgive him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then you used John--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that if the\Nlaw couldn't deal with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I would take\Njustice into my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure that John was happy\Nthat he avenged Masato too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't the only one who\Nwas sad when Masato-{\i1}kun {\i0}died!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how sad John was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said so yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, John still waits\Nfor Masato-{\i1}kun {\i0}in front of his door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think that\NMasato-{\i1}kun {\i0}would be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you used his\Nloyal dog to kill someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}.\NBullying is definitely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I actually do understand your\Nill will toward Maehara Takeshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But did you ever once think\Nabout the feelings of the dog
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you stupidly used as a\Nmurder tool to get revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John is saying that he still\Ncares for you, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try to understand that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:48.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:57.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:02.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:08.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:18.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:25.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:32.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:41.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:46.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they didn't kill John?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was taken in by one of\NSakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s relatives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all thanks to\NMori Kogoro, the great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But John doesn't live\Nat that house anymore, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.\NWe really liked him a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can always make\Nfriends with another dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Look at that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks just like John!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You appear to have\Nquite an exceptional dog, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm a dog-lover myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we talk about\Ndogs at that coffee shop over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sic 'im, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go start a relationship\Nwith a dog instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two took a bath together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.91,0:24:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,scrubbing each other's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nosebleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.87,0:24:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bath must've rushed the blood to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead if she finds out\Nwho I really am!
